title: Diamond 5 player looking for duo(s) to help get me back to Diamond 5
body:
IGN: iamthefox

Hey guys, made it to Diamond 5 last season, got placed in Plat 1 and have been struggling to get back over the border.
I generally main Mid/Jungle/Top, but am happy to support as well. Just looking for some fun people to help get me back :D

replies.body: Anyone? Seriously, just need ONE other player. I literally always carry as Malzahar
